=C2=A0Forget about balancing spiritual life with materia=
l life. Even with 2 materially oriented people, there can be big clashes of=
 personality. Bottomline is that no 2 persons have perfectly aligned agenda=
s. There is a clash between aspirations, expectations and agendas, as long =
as different people are living inter-dependent lives together. Husband may =
want to watch a game on TV and wife may want to go out to a movie. Husband =
may want to move to California for a better job and wife may want to stay p=
ut in New York where she has a great job. Husband may not want a child for =
a few more years and wife may want one. So many clashes occur even among ma=
terially oriented couples and one has to balance one's priorities, aspirati=
ons and agendas with those of others in one's life.
