=C2=A0
Why just between 2 people? Even within a single person, so many hope=
s, aspirations and desires lie latent as conditioning. They are all constan=
tly fighting with each other for the fuel (shakti) to advance further! The =
more time one spends thinking of some aspiration, it derives some shakti fr=
om one's mind to advance further! One needs to set priorities and not waste=
 time (and energy!) thinking unnecessary thoughts and dispersing mind's ene=
rgy in opposite directions..
=C2=A0
*=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=C2=A0=
